[49.943724, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mThe search has returned two available cruise options departing from Seattle to Alaska from July 10, 2025, to July 20, 2025:\r\n\r\n1. **Cruise ID: C12345**\r\n   - **Price:** $1,899.99\r\n   - **Room Options:** Interior, Oceanview, Balcony, and Suite (all available)\r\n\r\n2. **Cruise ID: C67890**\r\n   - **Price:** $2,199.99\r\n   - **Room Options:** Interior, Oceanview, Balcony, and Suite (all available)\r\n\r\nBoth cruises offer a range of cabin options, ensuring availability to suit different preferences and budgets for an Alaskan adventure.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[61.882492, "o", "\u001b[92mNeed data: data: Choose cruise and room option from these search results:\r\n1. Cruise ID: C12345, Price: $1899.99, Dates: July 10 - 20, 2025. Room Options: Interior, Oceanview, Balcony, Suite.\r\n2. Cruise ID: C67890, Price: $2199.99, Dates: July 10 - 20, 2025. Room Options: Interior, Oceanview, Balcony, Suite.\r\n\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[63.145155, "o", "\u001b[93mPlanner: Expedia: Book the cruise with ID C12345 for 2 people selecting the Balcony room option, departing on July 10, 2025, and returning on July 20, 2025.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
