[92.426894, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40m**Cruise Overview - ID: C12345**\r\n\r\n**Itinerary:**\r\n- **Day 1:** Depart Seattle, WA at 4:00 PM\r\n- **Day 2:** Day at Sea\r\n- **Day 3:** Ketchikan, AK (7:00 AM - 3:00 PM)\r\n- **Day 4:** Juneau, AK (7:00 AM - 1:30 PM)\r\n- **Day 5:** Skagway, AK (7:00 AM - 5:00 PM)\r\n- **Day 6:** Glacier Bay National Park, AK (6:00 AM - 3:00 PM)\r\n- **Day 7:** Day at Sea\r\n- **Day 8:** Victoria, BC, Canada (7:00 PM - 11:59 PM)\r\n- **Day 9:** Arrive Seattle, WA at 7:00 AM\r\n\r\n**Amenities:**\r\n- Swimming Pool\r\n- Spa and Wellness Center\r\n- Fitness Center\r\n- Multiple Dining Options\r\n- Casino\r\n- Live Entertainment\r\n- Children's Play Area\r\n- Shore Excursions\r\n\r\n**Activities:**\r\n- Wildlife Watching: Observe Alaska's diverse marine life.\r\n- Cultural Workshops: Engage with Alaska's indigenous cultural history.\r\n- Cooking Class: Learn cooking with Alaskan ingredients.\r\n\r\n**Special Events:**\r\n- **Welcome Party:** July 10, 2025, at 5:30 PM in Main Deck Lounge\r\n- **Farewell Dinner:** July 19, 2025, at 7:00 PM in Grand Dining Room\r\n\r\nEnjoy a memorable journey with exciting activities and luxurious amenities while exploring the stunning Alaskan scenery and ports.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[94.164401, "o", "\u001b[92mUser: user: Confirm cruise details and number of guests: C12345, Price: $1899.99, Itinerary includes ports like Ketchikan and Juneau, Amenities like Pool and Spa, for 2 people. Proceed?\u001b[0m\r\n"]
