[117.513314, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mFor your upcoming cruise (ID: C12345), explore these optional addons to enhance your experience:\r\n\r\n1. **Travel Insurance Package** - $149.99\r\n   - Comprehensive coverage for trip cancellations and medical emergencies.\r\n\r\n2. **Formal Dining Package** - $79.99\r\n   - Enjoy a reserved table at the Captain's Gala Dinner with a bottle of premium wine.\r\n\r\n3. **Spa Wellness Package** - $199.99\r\n   - Unlimited spa access and two 50-minute massages.\r\n\r\n4. **Special Occasion Celebration** - $99.99\r\n   - Celebrate birthdays or anniversaries with customized room decorations and a cake.\r\n\r\n5. **Wi-Fi Package** - $59.99\r\n   - Stay connected with unlimited internet access throughout the cruise. \r\n\r\nSelect these addons to tailor your cruise experience to your preferences and needs.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[118.731101, "o", "\u001b[92mUser: user: Confirm add-ons: Travel Insurance ($149.99), Formal Dining ($79.99), Spa Package ($199.99), Special Occasion Celebration ($99.99), Wi-Fi ($59.99). Would you like any?\u001b[0m\r\n"]
