[145.569374, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40m**Cruise Policies Summary:**\r\n\r\n- **Refund Policy:** \r\n  - Full refund for cancellations 90+ days before departure.\r\n  - 50% refund for cancellations 30-89 days prior.\r\n  - No refund for cancellations within 30 days of departure.\r\n\r\n- **Cancellation Policy:** \r\n  - Cancellations are manageable online or through customer service until departure day.\r\n  - Fees apply as per the refund schedule.\r\n\r\n- **Booking Policy:** \r\n  - Requires a 20% deposit to reserve.\r\n  - Full payment is due 60 days prior to departure.\r\n\r\n- **Change Policy:** \r\n  - Changes such as upgrades or date modifications allowed up to 60 days before departure, subject to fees and availability.\r\n\r\n- **Additional Policies:**\r\n  - **Travel Insurance:** Strongly recommended.\r\n  - **Onboard Purchases:** Charged to room account, payable by major credit cards.\r\n  - **Child Policy:** Free sailing for children under 3; activities and services available.\r\n  - **Accessibility:** Accommodations available; notify of any specific needs during booking.\r\n\r\nThis summary provides key details about refunds, cancellations, booking requirements, and additional policies to ensure a seamless travel experience.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[146.821511, "o", "\u001b[92mUser: user: Policies: Refund up to 90 days prior, 20% deposit, full payment 60 days before, and changeable bookings. Accept these policies?\u001b[0m\r\n"]
