[163.08466, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mFor Cruise ID C12345, the following payment options are available:\r\n\r\n1. **Full Payment**: Pay the total balance of $1,899.99 upfront to secure your booking immediately.\r\n\r\n2. **Partial Payment**: Make a 20% deposit of $379.99 to reserve your spot, with the remaining balance payable 60 days before departure.\r\n\r\n3. **Installment Payment**: Split the total amount into monthly installments until the final payment date.\r\n\r\nAdditional Options Available:\r\n\r\n- **Travel Insurance**: Add for $149.99 to cover cancellations and emergencies.\r\n- **Special Occasion Celebration**: Enhance your experience with decorations and a cake for $99.99.\r\n- **Wi-Fi Package**: Access unlimited internet for $59.99 during your cruise.\r\n\r\nAccepted payment methods include Visa, MasterCard, and American Express. Please note that the full payment should be settled 60 days before the departure to prevent booking cancellation.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[165.091741, "o", "\u001b[92mUser: user: Confirm payment method: Full Payment ($1,899.99), Partial Payment ($379.99 deposit), Installment Payment. Include Travel Insurance ($149.99) and Wi-Fi ($59.99)?\u001b[0m\r\n"]
