[241.743535, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mYour payment has been successfully processed for booking ID C12345. You used the Amex Gold card to pay a total of $2,108.97. This amount includes the cost of your trip and the following addons: Travel Insurance Package for $149.99, Special Occasion Celebration for $99.99, and a Wi-Fi Package for $59.99. Your itinerary is confirmed from July 10 to July 20, 2025, for a cruise from Seattle to Alaska. Enjoy your journey!\u001b[0m\r\n"]
