[380.94626, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mYour reservation has been successfully made for a cruise trip to Alaska, departing from Seattle. The trip is scheduled from July 10, 2025, to July 20, 2025, under Booking ID: C12345. Guests Alex Johnson and Jordan Smith will stay in a Balcony cabin, enjoying amenities such as Travel Insurance and a Wi-Fi package. The reservation includes access to facilities like the Swimming Pool, Spa, and Fitness Center, along with exciting activities such as Wildlife Watching and Cooking Classes. Enjoy your cruise!\u001b[0m\r\n"]
